%80%9A"><span class="nav-number">3.5.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">ping 测试主机之间网络连通</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#linux-%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE"><span class="nav-number">3.5.6.</span> <span class="nav-text">linux 网络环境配置</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86"><span class="nav-number">4.</span> <span class="nav-text">进程管理</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D"><span class="nav-number">4.0.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">进程的基本介绍</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B"><span class="nav-number">4.0.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">显示系统执行的进程</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#ps-%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%A3"><span class="nav-number">4.0.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">ps 指令详解</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%BB%88%E6%AD%A2%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B-kill-%E5%92%8C-killall"><span class="nav-number">4.0.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">终止进程 kill 和 killall</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E6%A0%91-pstree"><span class="nav-number">4.0.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">查看进程树 pstree</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1-Service-%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86"><span class="nav-number">5.</span> <span class="nav-text">服务(Service)管理</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#service-%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%EF%BC%9A"><span class="nav-number">5.0.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">service 管理指令：</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%90%8D"><span class="nav-number">5.0.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">查看服务名:</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%AB-runlevel"><span class="nav-number">5.0.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">服务的运行级别(runlevel):</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E"><span class="nav-number">5.0.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">开机的流程说明</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#chkconfig-%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4"><span class="nav-number">5.0.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">chkconfig 指令</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B"><span class="nav-number">5.0.6.</span> <span class="nav-text">动态监控进程</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5-netstat-%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81"><span class="nav-number">5.0.7.</span> <span class="nav-text">查看系统网络情况 netstat(重要)</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#RPM-%E5%92%8C-YUM"><span class="nav-number">5.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">RPM   和 YUM</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#rpm-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86"><span class="nav-number">5.1.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">rpm 包的管理</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#rpm-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4"><span class="nav-number">5.1.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">rpm 包的简单查询指令</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#rpm-%E5%8C%85%E5%90%8D%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%9A"><span class="nav-number">5.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">rpm 包名基本格式：</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#rpm-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%83%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%EF%BC%9A"><span class="nav-number">5.2.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">rpm 包的其它查询指令：</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%8D%B8%E8%BD%BD-rpm-%E5%8C%85%EF%BC%9A"><span class="nav-number">5.2.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">卸载 rpm 包：</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-rpm-%E5%8C%85%EF%BC%9A"><span class="nav-number">5.2.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">安装 rpm 包：</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#yum"><span class="nav-number">5.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">yum</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link"><span class="nav-number">5.4.</span> <span class="nav-text"></span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA-JavaEE-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83"><span class="nav-number">6.</span> <span class="nav-text">搭建 JavaEE 环境</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-JDK"><span class="nav-number">6.0.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">安装 JDK</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-tomcat"><span class="nav-number">6.0.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">安装 tomcat</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#Eclipse-%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85"><span class="nav-number">6.0.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">Eclipse 的安装</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#mysql-%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE"><span class="nav-number">6.0.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">mysql 的安装和配置</span></a></li><li cla