<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/Linux/1594039104006.png" alt="1594039104006"></p>
<h4 id="查看进程树-pstree"><a href="#查看进程树-pstree" class="headerlink" title="查看进程树 pstree"></a>查看进程树 pstree</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pstree [选项] ,可以更加直观的来看进程信息</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

