<p>查看是否安装成功</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysqladmin --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

